name: Jimi Hendrix Skull
description:
1942-1970 Still rockin after 41 years.

This Only50 print is like always limited to 50 shirts per design, You can purchase this shirt with the confidence that you probably won't seen anyone else walking around with it on.

This design is printed on a heather charcoal tultex brand shirt, and is printed using sublimation providing a softer feel than traditional plastisol  screen printing.

small-3
